<br>
I am usually on most evenings EST, and I should be on Sunday morning for a bit, if anyone wants to learn how humans speak.  (can't imagine why though, I am human and don't enjoy speaking with my kind most times)<br>
<br>
I would really like to learn Dark Elf, but I am happy to learn any language.  Knowledge is power.<br>
<br>
